subject: Automobile Racing
Automobiles
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Nascar’s arcane free-pass rule, also known as the lucky dog rule, allowed Kyle Busch to make up 5 laps and finish 9th after car troubles knocked him 12 miles off the pace.
